This directory contains the Mercury source code for the G12
XML-to-FlatZinc converter, xml2fzn.  This code requires
Mercury version 11.07.2 or above.

You can build xml2fzn with the following commands:

	mmc --make xml2fzn

This directory contains a modified copy of the XML parser from
the Mercury extras distribution.  This code is 
Copyright (C) 2000, 2001 The University of Melbourne.
(See the file XML.LICENSE for license terms.)
